%description
Read and write XES Files to create event log objects used by the 'bupaR'
framework. XES (Extensible Event Stream) is the `IEEE` standard for
storing and sharing event data (see
<http://standards.ieee.org/findstds/standard/1849-2016.html> for more
info).

